refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 public Ds\SetDs\Map::keys




  Returns a set containing all the keys of the map, in the same order.

  &reftitle.examples;

   Ds\Map::keys example


<?php
$map = new \Ds\Map(["a" => 1, "b" => 2, "c" => 3]);
var_dump($map->keys());
?>


   &example.outputs.similar;


object(Ds\Set)#2 (3) {
  [0]=>
  string(1) "a"
  [1]=>
  string(1) "b"
  [2]=>
  string(1) "c"
}
